{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01GaYTiAVEi9xube1BxuhvfX","type":"tool_result","content":"  1060→### What was done\n  1061→\n  1062→**social-tools — Comprehensive WCAG accessibility pass (PRs #44-#45, auto-merged)**\n  1063→- **Card component**: Added keyboard support (Enter/Space to activate) with focus ring for all clickable cards across the app\n  1064→- **ReactionButtons**: Added `aria-pressed` toggle state and `aria-label` with counts on both helpful/agree buttons\n  1065→- **SortPills**: Added `aria-pressed` on active pill, `role=\"group\"` with label on container\n  1066→- **StarRating**: Added `role=\"img\"` with descriptive `aria-label` (\"Rating: X.X out of 5 stars\")\n  1067→- **TrustBadges**: Added `aria-label` on badges, `aria-hidden` on decorative icons\n  1068→- **Header**: `aria-label` on nav, search form `role=\"search\"`, `sr-only` label for search input, `aria-current=\"page\"` on active nav link, `aria-label` on all nav links (for mobile icon-only view)\n  1069→- **App.tsx**: Wrapped page content in `<main>` landmark\n  1070→- **ReviewerSelector (ComparePage)**: Added `aria-haspopup=\"listbox\"`, `aria-expanded`, `role=\"listbox\"`/`role=\"option\"`, Escape key to close\n  1071→- **All back buttons** (4 pages): Added `aria-label`\n  1072→- **All search inputs** (3 locations): Associated `<label>` elements via `htmlFor`/`id`\n  1073→- **All filter pill groups** (3 pages): `role=\"group\"` with `aria-label`, `aria-pressed` on each pill\n  1074→- **40+ decorative Lucide icons**: Marked `aria-hidden=\"true\"` across 14 files\n  1075→- **Non-semantic interactive elements**: Replaced clickable `<span>`s with `<button>`s in ReviewCard and CirclePage FeedCard; wrapped clickable `<h2>` content in `<button>` on ComparePage\n  1076→- **Pagination (CategoryPage)**: Wrapped in `<nav aria-label=\"Pagination\">`, added `aria-label` on prev/next buttons\n  1077→- **Follow button (PersonPage)**: Added `aria-pressed` toggle